replies.body:
Whoever let that pup out needs to clean up the mess he left in the store dang it! {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 

We noticed this issue and that it's been affecting a number of players earlier today. We are working to fix the issue, and you can keep updated on our progress [**here**](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/lKb27XVQ-problems-getting-the-store-to-load).
